  "The linear model because it is simpler": "",
  "The linear model because r² = 0.72 is acceptable": "",
  "Neither model should be used": "",
  "The exponential model's higher r² and patternless residuals both confirm it captures the underlying decay pattern, while the linear model's curved residuals show it is inadequate.": "",
